enum.name: CATAxisSystemAxisType
enum.abstract: Specification of the axes of the coordinate system.

enum.name: CatConstraintAngleSector
enum.abstract: Special constraint property for angle constraints.

enum.name: CatConstraintDistConfig
enum.abstract: Special constraint configurations for distance constraints.

enum.name: CatConstraintMode
enum.abstract:
Constraint working mode
Part constraints can work in two modes: as constraints or as measurements.

enum.name: CatPartSurfaceElementsLocation
enum.abstract: Wireframe and surface elements location parameter's possible values.

class.name: AxisSystem
class.abstract: The object Axis System A axis system has got one origin point and three orthogonal axes, crossing at the origin point.

method.name: GetEulerAngles
method.abstract: Returns the Euler Angles of an axis system.

method.name: GetOrigin
method.abstract: Returns the coordinates X,Y,Z of the origin point of the axis system.

method.name: GetVectors
method.abstract: Returns the coordinates X,Y,Z of the axes X and Y of the axis system.

method.name: GetXAxis
method.abstract: Returns the coordinates X,Y,Z of the X axis of the axis system.

method.name: GetYAxis
method.abstract: Returns the coordinates X,Y,Z of the Y axis of the axis system.

method.name: GetZAxis
method.abstract: Returns the coordinates X,Y,Z of the Z axis of the axis system.

method.name: PutOrigin
method.abstract: Defines the coordinates X,Y,Z of the origin point of the axis system.

method.name: PutVectors
method.abstract: Defines the coordinates X,Y,Z of the axes X and Y of the axis system.

method.name: PutXAxis
method.abstract: Defines the coordinates X,Y,Z of the X axis of the axis system.

method.name: PutYAxis
method.abstract: Defines the coordinates X,Y,Z of the Y axis of the axis system.

method.name: PutZAxis
method.abstract: Defines the coordinates X,Y,Z of the Z axis of the axis system.

method.name: AxisRotationAngle
method.abstract: Returns the rotation angle of an axis system.

method.name: AxisRotationReference
method.abstract: Returns the reference for the axis rotation.

method.name: IsCurrent
method.abstract: Returns True if the axis system is the current one, else returns False.

method.name: OriginPoint
method.abstract: Returns or sets the geometric point which defines the origin of the axis system.

method.name: OriginType
method.abstract: Returns or sets the way the origin point is defined.

method.name: Type
method.abstract: Returns or sets the type of the axis system.

method.name: XAxisDirection
method.abstract: Reads or sets the geometric point, line or plane which defines the direction of the X axis.

method.name: XAxisType
method.abstract: Reads or sets the way the X axis is specified.

method.name: YAxisDirection
method.abstract: Reads or sets the geometric point, line or plane which defines the direction of the Y axis.

method.name: YAxisType
method.abstract: Reads or sets the way the Y axis is specified.

method.name: ZAxisDirection
method.abstract: Reads or sets the geometric point, line or plane which defines the direction of the Z axis.

method.name: ZAxisType
method.abstract: Reads or sets the way the Z axis is specified.

class.name: AxisSystems
class.abstract: A collection of all the AxisSystem objects contained in the part.

method.name: Add
method.abstract: Creates a new AxisSystem and adds it to the AxisSystems collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns an Axis System using its index or its name from the AxisSystems collection.

class.name: BiDimFeatEdge
class.abstract: 1-D boundary belonging to a feature whose topological result is two dimensional.

class.name: Bodies
class.abstract: A collection of all the Body objects contained in the part.

method.name: Add
method.abstract: Creates a new body and adds it to the Bodies collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a body using its index or its name from the Bodies collection.

class.name: Body
class.abstract: The object that manages a sequence of shapes, a set of sketches, a set of hybrid bodies, a set of ordered geometrical sets and a set of hybrid shapes.

method.name: InsertHybridShape
method.abstract: Insert a hybrid shape to the body.

method.name: HybridBodies
method.abstract: Returns the body's HybridBodies collection.

method.name: HybridShapes
method.abstract: Returns the list of hybrid shapes included in the body.

method.name: InBooleanOperation
method.abstract: Returns True if the body is involved in a boolean operation, else returns False.

method.name: OrderedGeometricalSets
method.abstract: Returns the body's OrderedGeometricalSets collection.

method.name: Shapes
method.abstract: Returns the body's Shapes collection.

method.name: Sketches
method.abstract: Returns the body's Sketches collection.

class.name: Boundary
class.abstract: Topological cell, such as a face, an edge or a vertex.

class.name: Constraint
class.abstract: A geometric constraint set for geometric elements of a part, a sketch, or a product.

method.name: Activate
method.abstract: Unsuppresses a constraint for the update process.

method.name: Deactivate
method.abstract: Suppresses the constraint from being updated.

method.name: GetConstraintElement
method.abstract: Reads an element of a constraint.

method.name: GetConstraintVisuLocation
method.abstract: Returns the constraint visualisation location.

method.name: IsInactive
method.abstract: Indicates whether a constraint is suppressed from the update process.

method.name: SetConstraintElement
method.abstract: Replaces an element of a constraint.

method.name: SetConstraintVisuLocation
method.abstract: Sets a new location for the constraint visualization.

method.name: AngleSector
method.abstract: Returns or sets the constraint angle (or angular) sector.

method.name: Dimension
method.abstract: Returns the constraint dimension.

method.name: DistanceConfig
method.abstract: Returns or sets the distance constraint configuration.

method.name: DistanceDirection
method.abstract: Returns or sets the distance constraint direction.

method.name: Mode
method.abstract: Returns or sets the constraint driving mode.

method.name: Orientation
method.abstract: Returns or sets the constraint orientation.

method.name: ReferenceAxis
method.abstract: Returns or sets the constraint reference axis.

method.name: ReferenceType
method.abstract: Returns or sets the constraint reference type.

method.name: Side
method.abstract: Returns or sets the constraint side.

method.name: Status
method.abstract: Returns the constraint status.

method.name: Type
method.abstract: Returns the constraint type.

class.name: Constraints
class.abstract: A collection of all geometric constraints set on a part, a sketch, or a product.

method.name: AddBiEltCst
method.abstract: Creates a new constraint applying to two geometric elements and adds it to the Constraints collection.

method.name: AddMonoEltCst
method.abstract: Creates a new constraint applying to a single geometric element and adds it to the Constraints collection.

method.name: AddTriEltCst
method.abstract: Creates a new constraint applying to three geometric elements and adds it to the Constraints collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a constraint using its index or its name from the Constraints collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes a constraint from the Constraints collection.

method.name: BrokenConstraintsCount
method.abstract: Returns the number of broken constraints from the Constraints collection.

method.name: UnUpdatedConstraintsCount
method.abstract: Returns the number of unupdated constraints from the Constraints collection.

class.name: CylindricalFace
class.abstract: 2-D boundary with a cylindrical geometry.

method.name: GetOrigin
method.abstract: Returns the origin of the cylindrical face axis.

class.name: Edge
class.abstract: 1-D boundary.

class.name: Face
class.abstract: 2-D boundary.

class.name: Factory
class.abstract: Abstract object gathering behaviours of all objects being a factory.

class.name: FixTogether
class.abstract: The object that manages a sequence of products or fixTogethers.

method.name: AddFixTogether
method.abstract: Add a fixTogether to a FixTogether.

method.name: AddProduct
method.abstract: Add a product to a FixTogether.

method.name: GetFixTogether
method.abstract: Returns a FixTogether using its index or its name in the FixTogether.

method.name: GetProduct
method.abstract: Returns a Product using its index or its name in the FixTogether.

method.name: RemoveFixTogether
method.abstract: Removes a FixTogether from the FixTogether.

method.name: RemoveProduct
method.abstract: Removes a Product from the FixTogether.

method.name: FixTogethersCount
method.abstract: Returns the number of FixTogether entities in the FixTogether.

method.name: ProductsCount
method.abstract: Returns the number of products fixed together in the FixTogether.

class.name: FixTogethers
class.abstract: A collection of all the FixTogether objects contained in the product.

method.name: Add
method.abstract: Creates a new FixTogether and adds it to the FixTogethers collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a FixTogether using its index or its name from the FixTogethers collection.

method.name: Remove
method.abstract: Removes a FixTogether from the FixTogethers collection.

class.name: GeometricElements
class.abstract: A collection of all geometric elements contained in a part or a sketch.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a geometric element using its index or its name from the GeometricElements collection.

class.name: HybridBodies
class.abstract: A collection of the HybridBody objects.

method.name: Add
method.abstract: Creates a new hybrid body and adds it to the HybridBodies collection.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns a body using its index or its name from the Bodies collection.

class.name: HybridBody
class.abstract: The object is a hybrid body.

method.name: AppendHybridShape
method.abstract: Appends a hybrid shape to the hybrid body.

method.name: Bodies
method.abstract: Returns the hybrid body's Bodies collection.

method.name: GeometricElements
method.abstract: Returns the list of geometrical elements included in the hybrid body.

method.name: HybridBodies
method.abstract: Returns the hybrid body's HybridBodies collection.

method.name: HybridShapes
method.abstract: Returns the list of hybrid shapes included in the hybrid body.

method.name: HybridSketches

class.name: HybridShape
class.abstract: Represents the hybrid shape object.

method.name: AppendHybridShape
method.abstract: Appends a hybrid shape to another hybrid shape.

method.name: Compute
method.abstract: Computes the result of the hybrid shape.

method.name: Thickness
method.abstract: Returns the thickness of the hybrid shape.

class.name: HybridShapeInstance
class.abstract: The interface to access a CATIAHybridShapeInstance.

method.name: GetInput
method.abstract: Gets an input of a hybrid shape instance by its name.

method.name: GetInputData
method.abstract: Gets an input of a shape instance by its name.

method.name: GetInputDataFromPosition
method.abstract: Gets an input of a hybrid shape instance from its position.

method.name: GetInputFromPosition
method.abstract: Gets an input of a hybrid shape instance from its position.

method.name: GetOutput
method.abstract: Gets a Ouput by its name.

method.name: GetOutputFromPosition
method.abstract: Gets a Ouput from its position.

method.name: GetParameter
method.abstract: Gets a parameter of a hybrid shape instance by its name.

method.name: GetParameterFromPosition
method.abstract: Gets a parameter of a hybrid shape instance from its position.

method.name: PutInput
method.abstract: Defines an input of a hybrid shape instance.

method.name: PutInputData
method.abstract: Defines an input of a shape instance.

method.name: InputsCount
method.abstract: Returns the number of Inputs.

method.name: OutputsCount
method.abstract: Returns the number of Outputs.

method.name: ParametersCount

class.name: HybridShapes
class.abstract: The collection of the HybridShapes making up a body.

class.name: InstanceFactory
class.abstract: Represents the CATIAInstanceFactory.

method.name: AddInstance
method.abstract: Creates a new instance of a shape or hybrid shape.

method.name: InstantiationMode
method.abstract: Sets the mode of instantiation to "Inside" or "After".
